==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inexpugnable
<hw>In`ex*pug"na*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>inexpugnabilis</ets>: cf. F. <ets>inexpugnable</ets>. See
<er>In-</er> not, and <er>Expugnable</er>.]</ety> <def>Incapable of
being subdued by force; impregnable; unconquerable.</def>
<rj><au>Burke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A fortress, <qex>inexpugnable</qex> by the arts of war.</q>
<rj><qau>Milman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inexpugnably</ent>⟦br⟧
